    <title type="html"><![CDATA[JSP中怎样输出\r\n到textarea中]]></title>
    <link href="http://codemany.com/blog/2005/01/12/how-to-insert-line-breaks-into-textarea-with-jsp/"/>
    <updated>2005-01-12T12:47:51+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://codemany.com/blog/2005/01/12/how-to-insert-line-breaks-into-textarea-with-jsp</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>测试代码如下：</p>

<p>```
&lt;%</p>

<pre><code>String str = "first line\r\nsecond line";
</code></pre>

<p>%></p>

<p><body></p>

<pre><code>&lt;textarea id="editor" name="editor"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;;
</code></pre>

<p></body></p>

<script language="javascript">
<!–-
    var editor = document.getElementById('editor');
    editor.value = '<%= str.replaceAll("\r\n", "\\\\r\\\\n") %>';
//-–>
</script>


<p>```</p>
